description: This dataset contains URLs and their associated binary content, enabling the analysis and retrieval of web resources. It serves as a foundational resource for web data management and content analysis.

metadata.description: Unique identifier for each record in the dataset.
The web address of the resource; It points to the location of the sitemap in XML format.
Binary content of the resource; Stores the raw data of the file, which can include various formats such as XML, JSON, or images.
